flowchart TD
    Start([Start: Teacher receives email from Principal/Secretary OR recognizes end of quarter/semester is near])

    D1{Is it time to finalize grades?}
    S2[Step 2: Log in to PowerSchool with valid username and password]
    S3[Step 3: Open PowerTeacher Pro under a currently taught class]
    S4[Step 4: Navigate to Grading → Score Sheet, cycle through all classes, verify all quarter/semester grades line by line]
    S5[Step 5: Open Settings → Traditional Grade Calculations, select class, choose Actions → Edit, verify grade weights]
    S6[Step 6: Save grade calculation changes before exiting]
    S7[Step 7: Navigate to Grading → Grades → Traditional to view final quarter/semester grade]
    D2{Is the final grade correct?}
    S8[Step 8: Mark 'Final Grade Status' as complete at bottom of screen]
    D3{Are all classes finalized?}
    S10[Step 10: Send email to Secretary confirming grades are stored, then log out]

    End([End: All grades stored in PowerSchool and email confirmation sent to Secretary])
    EndNoAction([End: No action needed])

    Start --> D1
    D1 -- Yes --> S2
    D1 -- No --> EndNoAction
    S2 --> S3
    S3 --> S4
    S4 --> S5
    S5 --> S6
    S6 --> S7
    S7 --> D2
    D2 -- Yes --> S8
    D2 -- No --> S4
    S8 --> D3
    D3 -- Yes --> S10
    D3 -- No --> S7
    S10 --> End

